ient Greece. Perfect in and out of the classroom as well as for theatrical performance, this faithful translation succeeds like no other.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 7aPOETRY / Ancient & Classical.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDTL Humanities 2020z978311073776908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishz978311061076508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural and Area Stud. 2019 Englishz978311061036908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural and Area Studies 2019z9783110606348oZDB-23-DKU08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUCA Complete eBook-Package 2019z978311065207908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Complete eBook-Package 2019z978311066763940uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/9780520973756?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520973756423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520973756/original  a978-3-11-061036-9  EBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural and Area Stud. 2019 Englishb2019  a978-3-11-061076-5  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishb2019  a978-3-11-065207-9  UCA Complete eBook-Package 2019b2019  a978-3-11-066763-9  University of California Press Complete eBook-Package 2019b2019  a978-3-11-073776-9  DTL Humanities 2020b2020  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2019  aZDB-23-DKUb2019